---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { platforms, testFlightUrl } from "../config/downloads";
---

<BaseLayout title="下载">
  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-display-small-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-display-small-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-display-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-2">下载 Luotopia</h1>
      <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-line)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] mb-4">选择你的平台，获取最新版本</p>
      <p id="latest-meta" class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] mb-12">正在从 GitHub Releases 加载…</p>

      <div id="platform-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
        {platforms.map((p) => (
          <div
            class="platform-card rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-medium)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low-dark)] p-5 flex flex-col"
            data-platform={p.id}
            data-external-url={p.externalUrl ?? ""}
            data-external-label={p.externalLabel ?? ""}
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] text-3xl mb-3">{p.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">{p.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] mt-1">{p.desc}</p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 items-center platform-badges">
              <span class="platform-status inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)]">
                {p.externalUrl ? (p.id === "ios" ? "TestFlight 内测" : p.externalLabel) : "加载中…"}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class:list={["platform-assets", "mt-3", "space-y-1.5", !p.externalUrl && "hidden"]}>
              {p.externalUrl && (
                <a
                  href={p.externalUrl}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline no-underline"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">open_in_new</span>
                  <span>{p.externalLabel ?? "外部安装"}</span>
                </a>
              )}
            </div>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">{p.note}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-medium)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low-dark)] p-6">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-4">安装说明</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)]">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">Android</h4>
            <p>按 ABI 分发包（与 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">build-release.bat --split-per-abi</code> 一致）：优先选标有「推荐」的 <strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">arm64-v8a</strong>（近年金属机）；老设备用 armeabi-v7a。下载 APK 后直接安装；如提示「未知来源」，请在系统设置中允许安装。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">iOS</h4>
            <p>iOS 版本通过 TestFlight 分发。打开
              <a href={testFlightUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">TestFlight 加入链接</a>
              即可申请内测。由于 Apple 政策限制，非越狱设备需通过 TestFlight 安装。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">Windows</h4>
            <p>Release 提供 <strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">x64 便携 zip</strong>（解压运行 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">luotopia.exe</code>）与 <strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">MSIX</strong>。多数 PC 选标有「推荐」的 <strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">x64 / amd64</strong>。需 Windows 10 1809 及以上。未签名包可能触发 SmartScreen，选「仍要运行」；MSIX 无签时需开启开发人员模式或允许旁加载。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">Linux</h4>
            <p>每个 Release 按<strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">架构</strong>（x64 / arm64）与<strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">格式</strong>发布（均为 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">--release</code>，无 debug 符号）：</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">tar.gz</strong> — 便携目录，推荐通用；标「推荐」的多为 x64/amd64</li>
              <li><strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">AppImage</strong> — 单文件运行（需 FUSE 或直接可执行）</li>
              <li><strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">deb</strong> — Debian/Ubuntu：<code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">sudo apt install ./luotopia-*-linux-*.deb</code></li>
              <li><strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">flatpak</strong> — 本地 bundle（若 CI 成功生成）：<code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">flatpak install --user ./luotopia-*-linux-*.flatpak</code></li>
            </ul>
            <pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code>tar -xzf luotopia-*-linux-x64.tar.gz &amp;&amp; ./luotopia/luotopia
# 或
chmod +x luotopia-*-linux-x64.AppImage &amp;&amp; ./luotopia-*-linux-x64.AppImage</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">依赖较新 glibc + GTK3。arm64 在 GitHub ARM runner 上原生构建。手动重跑 CI 可选架构（x64/arm64/both）与格式（tar,appimage,deb,flatpak）。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-medium)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low-dark)] p-6">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-2">高级用户 / 包管理器</h2>
        <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] mb-4">面向喜欢 CLI 安装、可复现升级的用户。资产随每个 GitHub Release 发布（含 prerelease）。</p>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)]">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">Scoop</h4>
            <p class="mb-2">从对应 Release 的清单直接安装（将 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">&lt;tag&gt;</code> 换成版本，如 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">v1.0.0+2</code>）：</p>
            <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code>scoop install https://github.com/ClosedWHU/Luotopia/releases/download/&lt;tag&gt;/scoop-luotopia.json</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">清单基于便携 zip；升级可重新 install 新 tag 的 json，或自行维护 bucket。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">winget</h4>
            <p class="mb-2">官方社区源合并前，可用 Release 里的草稿清单本地验证：</p>
            <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code># 下载 winget-ClosedWHU.Luotopia*.yaml 后
winget install --manifest .\path\to\manifests\folder</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2">合并到 <a href="https://github.com/microsoft/winget-pkgs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">microsoft/winget-pkgs</a> 之后：</p>
            <pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code>winget install ClosedWHU.Luotopia</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">当前清单默认指向 zip 便携包；有签名 MSIX 后再可改为 MSIX 安装器以改善 SmartScreen 体验。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">MSIX 旁加载</h4>
            <p>下载 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">*-windows-x64.msix</code> 后双击安装，或：</p>
            <pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code>Add-AppxPackage .\luotopia-*-windows-x64.msix</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">未提供 Windows 代码签名证书时为未签名包。可选在仓库配置 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">WINDOWS_PFX_BASE64</code> / <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">WINDOWS_PFX_PASSWORD</code> 以在 CI 中签名。传统 WiX MSI 暂不维护。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-1">Linux 包格式速查</h4>
            <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] px-3 py-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]"><code># 架构：x64 或 arm64（文件名含 linux-x64 / linux-arm64）
sudo apt install ./luotopia-*-linux-x64.deb
chmod +x ./luotopia-*-linux-x64.AppImage &amp;&amp; ./luotopia-*-linux-x64.AppImage
flatpak install --user ./luotopia-*-linux-x64.flatpak</code></pre>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">deb 控制字段 Architecture 为 amd64/arm64；Release 文件名用 <code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">x64</code>/<code class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">arm64</code> 以便官网识别。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center mb-20">
        <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">
          你也可以直接访问
          <a href="https://github.com/ClosedWHU/Luotopia/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">GitHub Releases</a>
          查看所有历史版本和发布说明。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="changelog">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-headline-small-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-headline-small-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-headline-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] mb-2">更新日志</h2>
        <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-large-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] mb-8">来自 GitHub Releases 的发布历史</p>

        <div id="changelog-list" class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">加载中…</p>
        </div>

        <div id="changelog-pager" class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hidden">
          <button type="button" id="changelog-prev" class="state-layer rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-full)] px-5 py-2 border border-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] bg-transparent cursor-pointer font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-weight)] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">上一页</button>
          <span id="changelog-page-label" class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]"></span>
          <button type="button" id="changelog-next" class="state-layer rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-full)] px-5 py-2 border border-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] bg-transparent cursor-pointer font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-weight)] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">下一页</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  (function () {
    const PER_PAGE = 5;
    let page = 1;
    let hasNext = false;
    let hasPrev = false;

    const latestMeta = document.getElementById("latest-meta");
    const listEl = document.getElementById("changelog-list");
    const pager = document.getElementById("changelog-pager");
    const prevBtn = document.getElementById("changelog-prev");
    const nextBtn = document.getElementById("changelog-next");
    const pageLabel = document.getElementById("changelog-page-label");

    function formatSize(bytes) {
      if (!bytes && bytes !== 0) return "";
      if (bytes < 1024) return bytes + " B";
      if (bytes < 1024 * 1024) return (bytes / 1024).toFixed(1) + " KB";
      return (bytes / (1024 * 1024)).toFixed(1) + " MB";
    }

    /** Split name so UI can truncate base while keeping suffix (e.g. .tar.gz) visible. */
    function splitFilename(name) {
      const n = String(name || "");
      const multi = n.match(/(\.(tar\.gz|tgz))$/i);
      if (multi) {
        return { base: n.slice(0, -multi[1].length), ext: multi[1] };
      }
      const i = n.lastIndexOf(".");
      if (i > 0) return { base: n.slice(0, i), ext: n.slice(i) };
      return { base: n, ext: "" };
    }

    function formatDate(iso) {
      if (!iso) return "";
      try {
        return new Date(iso).toLocaleDateString("zh-CN", { year: "numeric", month: "short", day: "numeric" });
      } catch {
        return iso.slice(0, 10);
      }
    }

    function escapeHtml(s) {
      return String(s)
        .replaceAll("&", "&amp;")
        .replaceAll("<", "&lt;")
        .replaceAll(">", "&gt;")
        .replaceAll('"', "&quot;");
    }

    /** Inline markdown after HTML escape: **bold**, `code`, [text](url) */
    function formatInline(s) {
      return s
        .replace(/\[([^\]]+)\]\((https?:\/\/[^)\s]+)\)/g, (_, t, u) => {
          return `<a href="${u}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">${t}</a>`;
        })
        .replace(/`([^`]+)`/g, '<code class="px-1 rounded-[4px] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)] text-[0.9em]">$1</code>')
        .replace(/\*\*([^*]+)\*\*/g, '<strong class="font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">$1</strong>');
    }

    /** Release notes markdown: headings, lists, hr, paragraphs */
    function formatBody(body) {
      if (!body) return '<p class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">暂无说明</p>';
      const lines = escapeHtml(body).split(/\r?\n/);
      const html = [];
      let inList = false;
      const closeList = () => {
        if (inList) {
          html.push("</ul>");
          inList = false;
        }
      };
      for (const raw of lines) {
        const line = raw.replace(/\s+$/, "");
        if (line.trim() === "") {
          closeList();
          html.push('<div class="h-2"></div>');
          continue;
        }
        if (/^---+$/.test(line.trim()) || /^\*\*\*+$/.test(line.trim())) {
          closeList();
          html.push('<hr class="my-3 border-[var(--md-sys-color-outline-variant)]" />');
          continue;
        }
        const h = line.match(/^(#{1,4})\s+(.+)$/);
        if (h) {
          closeList();
          const level = h[1].length;
          const text = formatInline(h[2]);
          if (level === 1) {
            html.push(
              `<h3 class="mt-4 mb-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${text}</h3>`,
            );
          } else if (level === 2) {
            html.push(
              `<h3 class="mt-4 mb-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-medium-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${text}</h3>`,
            );
          } else {
            html.push(
              `<h4 class="mt-3 mb-1.5 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-small-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${text}</h4>`,
            );
          }
          continue;
        }
        const item = line.match(/^\s*[-*•]\s+(.+)/);
        if (item) {
          if (!inList) {
            html.push('<ul class="space-y-1.5 my-2 pl-0 list-none">');
            inList = true;
          }
          html.push(
            `<li class="flex gap-2 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)]"><span class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] shrink-0 select-none">•</span><span class="min-w-0">${formatInline(item[1])}</span></li>`,
          );
          continue;
        }
        closeList();
        html.push(
          `<p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)]">${formatInline(line)}</p>`,
        );
      }
      closeList();
      return html.join("");
    }

    function prereleaseBadge() {
      return `<span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-error-container)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-error-container)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)]">测试版</span>`;
    }

    function stableBadge(text) {
      return `<span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-primary-container)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-primary-container)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)]">${escapeHtml(text)}</span>`;
    }

    function mutedBadge(text) {
      return `<span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)]">${escapeHtml(text)}</span>`;
    }

    function applyExternalLink(card, statusText) {
      const status = card.querySelector(".platform-status");
      const assetsEl = card.querySelector(".platform-assets");
      if (!status || !assetsEl) return;

      const externalUrl = card.getAttribute("data-external-url") || "";
      const externalLabel = card.getAttribute("data-external-label") || "外部安装";
      const id = card.getAttribute("data-platform");

      status.className =
        "platform-status inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-high-dark)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)]";

      if (externalUrl) {
        status.textContent = id === "ios" ? "TestFlight 内测" : statusText;
        assetsEl.classList.remove("hidden");
        assetsEl.innerHTML = `<a href="${escapeHtml(externalUrl)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline no-underline">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">open_in_new</span>
            <span>${escapeHtml(externalLabel)}</span>
          </a>`;
      } else {
        status.textContent = statusText;
        assetsEl.classList.add("hidden");
        assetsEl.innerHTML = "";
      }
    }

    /** Enrich iOS card with App Store / Connect lookup (version / release date). */
    async function loadAppStoreIos() {
      const card = document.querySelector('.platform-card[data-platform="ios"]');
      if (!card) return;

      let info = null;
      try {
        const r = await fetch("/api/appstore/latest");
        if (r.ok) info = await r.json();
      } catch {
        /* ignore */
      }

      if (!info || info.error || !info.version) return;

      const badges = card.querySelector(".platform-badges");
      const assetsEl = card.querySelector(".platform-assets");
      const noteEl = card.querySelector("p.mt-2");
      if (!badges || !assetsEl) return;

      const isTf = info.channel === "testflight" || info.source === "appstoreconnect";
      const channelLabel = isTf ? "TestFlight" : "App Store";

      badges.innerHTML = "";
      if (isTf) {
        badges.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", prereleaseBadge().replace("测试版", "TestFlight"));
      }
      badges.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", stableBadge(info.version));
      badges.insertAdjacentHTML(
        "beforeend",
        mutedBadge(info.publishedAt ? formatDate(info.publishedAt) : channelLabel),
      );

      const externalUrl = card.getAttribute("data-external-url") || "";
      const externalLabel = card.getAttribute("data-external-label") || "加入 TestFlight";
      const storeUrl = info.storeUrl || "";
      const links = [];
      if (storeUrl && !isTf) {
        links.push(
          `<a href="${escapeHtml(storeUrl)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline no-underline">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">storefront</span>
            <span>App Store</span>
          </a>`,
        );
      }
      if (externalUrl) {
        links.push(
          `<a href="${escapeHtml(externalUrl)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-1 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline no-underline">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">open_in_new</span>
            <span>${escapeHtml(externalLabel)}</span>
          </a>`,
        );
      }
      assetsEl.classList.remove("hidden");
      assetsEl.innerHTML = links.join("");

      if (noteEl) {
        noteEl.textContent =
          `${channelLabel} ${info.version}` +
          (info.publishedAt ? ` · ${formatDate(info.publishedAt)}` : "") +
          (info.minOsVersion ? ` · 需 iOS ${info.minOsVersion}+` : "");
      }
    }

    async function loadLatest() {
      // Prefer newest including prerelease so testers see pre builds; badge will mark it
      let release = null;
      try {
        const r = await fetch("/api/releases/latest?prerelease=1");
        if (r.ok) release = await r.json();
      } catch { /* ignore */ }

      if (!release || release.error) {
        if (latestMeta) latestMeta.textContent = "暂时无法获取最新版本，请前往 GitHub Releases。";
        document.querySelectorAll(".platform-card").forEach((card) => {
          applyExternalLink(card, "暂无数据");
        });
        return;
      }

      const verLabel = release.version || release.tag || release.title;
      if (latestMeta) {
        latestMeta.innerHTML =
          `当前最新：<strong class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${escapeHtml(verLabel)}</strong>` +
          (release.prerelease ? ` ${prereleaseBadge()}` : "") +
          (release.publishedAt ? ` · ${formatDate(release.publishedAt)}` : "") +
          (release.htmlUrl
            ? ` · <a href="${escapeHtml(release.htmlUrl)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">Release 详情</a>`
            : "");
      }

      const byPlatform = {};
      for (const a of release.assets || []) {
        const p = a.platform || "other";
        if (!byPlatform[p]) byPlatform[p] = [];
        byPlatform[p].push(a);
      }

      document.querySelectorAll(".platform-card").forEach((card) => {
        const id = card.getAttribute("data-platform");
        const badges = card.querySelector(".platform-badges");
        const assetsEl = card.querySelector(".platform-assets");
        const assets = byPlatform[id] || [];

        if (!badges || !assetsEl) return;

        if (assets.length === 0) {
          const fallback = release.prerelease ? `测试版 ${verLabel}` : `最新 ${verLabel}`;
          applyExternalLink(card, fallback);
          return;
        }

        badges.innerHTML = "";
        if (release.prerelease) {
          badges.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", prereleaseBadge());
        }
        badges.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", stableBadge(verLabel));

        const installers = assets.filter((a) => !a.meta);
        assetsEl.classList.remove("hidden");
        assetsEl.innerHTML = installers
          .map((a) => {
            const title =
              a.label ||
              [a.archLabel || a.arch, a.formatLabel].filter(Boolean).join(" · ") ||
              a.name;
            const rec = a.recommended
              ? `<span class="shrink-0 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-small)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-primary-container)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-primary-container)] text-[10px] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-weight)] leading-none">推荐</span>`
              : "";
            const { base, ext } = splitFilename(a.name);
            return `<a href="${escapeHtml(a.url)}" title="${escapeHtml(a.name)}" class="flex items-start gap-1.5 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline no-underline" download>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base shrink-0 mt-0.5">download</span>
                <span class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                  <span class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5">
                    <span class="font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${escapeHtml(title)}</span>
                    ${rec}
                  </span>
                  <span class="flex min-w-0 items-baseline text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] text-[11px] mt-0.5">
                    <span class="truncate min-w-0">${escapeHtml(base)}</span>
                    <span class="shrink-0">${escapeHtml(ext)}</span>
                    <span class="shrink-0"> · ${formatSize(a.size)}</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </a>`;
          })
          .join("");
      });
    }

    async function loadChangelog(p) {
      if (!listEl) return;
      listEl.innerHTML = `<p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">加载中…</p>`;
      try {
        const r = await fetch(`/api/releases?page=${p}&per_page=${PER_PAGE}`);
        if (!r.ok) throw new Error("HTTP " + r.status);
        const data = await r.json();
        page = data.page || p;
        hasNext = !!data.hasNext;
        hasPrev = !!data.hasPrev || page > 1;
        const items = data.items || [];

        if (items.length === 0) {
          listEl.innerHTML = `<p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">暂无发布记录。请访问 <a href="https://github.com/ClosedWHU/Luotopia/releases" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Releases</a>。</p>`;
        } else {
          listEl.innerHTML = items
            .map((rel) => {
              const ver = rel.version || rel.tag || rel.title;
              const assetList = (rel.assets || []).filter((a) => !a.meta);
              const assets =
                assetList.length > 0
                  ? `<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">${assetList
                      .map((a) => {
                        const label =
                          a.label ||
                          [a.platform, a.archLabel || a.arch, a.formatLabel]
                            .filter(Boolean)
                            .join(" · ") ||
                          a.name;
                        const rec = a.recommended ? " · 推荐" : "";
                        return `<a href="${escapeHtml(a.url)}" title="${escapeHtml(a.name)}" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1 rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-full)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-dark)] text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-label-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] no-underline hover:underline" download>
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">download</span>${escapeHtml(label + rec)}
                          </a>`;
                      })
                      .join("")}</div>`
                  : "";
              return `<article class="rounded-[var(--md-sys-shape-corner-medium)] bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low)] dark:bg-[var(--md-sys-color-surface-container-low-dark)] p-6">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                  <h3 class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-size)] leading-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-line)] font-[var(--md-sys-typescale-title-large-weight)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface)]">${escapeHtml(ver)}</h3>
                  ${rel.prerelease ? prereleaseBadge() : ""}
                  <span class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] ml-auto">${formatDate(rel.publishedAt)}</span>
                </div>
                ${rel.title && rel.title !== ver && rel.title !== rel.tag ? `<p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)] mb-3">${escapeHtml(rel.title)}</p>` : ""}
                <div class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant)]">${formatBody(rel.body)}</div>
                ${assets}
                ${rel.htmlUrl ? `<p class="mt-4 text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-small-size)]"><a href="${escapeHtml(rel.htmlUrl)}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline">在 GitHub 上查看</a></p>` : ""}
              </article>`;
            })
            .join("");
        }

        if (pager && prevBtn && nextBtn && pageLabel) {
          pager.classList.remove("hidden");
          prevBtn.disabled = !hasPrev;
          nextBtn.disabled = !hasNext;
          pageLabel.textContent = `第 ${page} 页`;
        }
      } catch {
        listEl.innerHTML = `<p class="text-[length:var(--md-sys-typescale-body-medium-size)] text-[var(--md-sys-color-outline)]">加载失败（本地开发需部署 Pages Functions，或配置 GITHUB_TOKEN）。请访问 <a href="https://github.com/ClosedWHU/Luotopia/releases" class="text-[var(--md-sys-color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Releases</a>。</p>`;
        pager?.classList.add("hidden");
      }
    }

    prevBtn?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      if (page > 1) loadChangelog(page - 1);
    });
    nextBtn?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      if (hasNext) loadChangelog(page + 1);
    });

    loadLatest().then(() => loadAppStoreIos());
    loadChangelog(1);
  })();
</script>
